---
title: Scrambled Egg Sandos with Gouda, Sweet Potato Rounds & Arugula Salad
description: Looking for a dynamic dinner, hearty breakfast, or a brunch crowd-pleaser? Meet the scrambled egg sando. Toasty buns are slathered with an herby aïoli, then filled with arugula, sliced tomato, and scrambled eggs topped with melty gouda. Roasted sweet potato rounds star on the side, along with a lemony arugula salad, for what’s bound to be the most important (and delicious) meal of the day!
